{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Weird Wormholes is a casual game about traveling through wormholes to try and get back home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your ship to mine planets for resources and process these resources into components to enable your travels or to trade with local Space Stations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Local Space Stations will sell you upgrades to speed up and assist you in your endeavors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The idea behind the game is centered around a relaxing and casual game play. There is no way to die or loose, just more efficient ways of doing tasks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328020/extras/titlescreen.png?t=1735554462\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In-game features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mine planets for resources</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Refine resources using your ships onboard smelter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use refined resources to manufacture items to enable you travels through wormholes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Trade with local space stations to upgrade your ship</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Several purchasable incremental-like generators you can invest in to passively improve your ship</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"100 Planets Discovered","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3328020/8af74f830542558cf9145401c6fc6e77ba4b827b.jpg"},{"name":"1000 Planets Discovered","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3328020/f03e73199749e0d7d6291a4f5adf1bdc31e74893.jpg"},{"name":"5000 Planets Discovered","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3328020/23fbe5a40f5e03da725c1fb87c15bf73faab0adf.jpg"},{"name":"25k Planets Discovered","path":"https://cdn.akama